\det(A')=\sum_{\sigma \in S_n}{\rm sgn}\; \tau(\tau\sigma)\; a_{1\tau\sigma (1)}\cdots a_{n\sigma (n)} \\= \sum_{\sigma' \in S_n}{\rm sgn}\; \tau \sigma'\; a_{1\sigma'(1)}\cdots a_{n\sigma'(n)}
